00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:55.770 align:middle line:84%
Her research has repeatedly
shown the profound effect

00:00:55.770 --> 00:00:58.440 align:middle line:90%
thoughts have on reality.

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:02.790 align:middle line:10%
>> We're all a batch of
vibrating packets of energy.

00:01:02.790 --> 00:01:05.400 align:middle line:10%
