in just those two provinces.

00:03:41.940 --> 00:03:45.690 align:middle line:10%
But in my mind, the most
important and interesting part

00:03:45.690 --> 00:03:50.250 align:middle line:10%
of the study was that the
Arabs and the Americans

00:03:50.250 --> 00:03:54.900 align:middle line:10%
