on my instant messenger pages.

00:03:54.900 --> 00:03:57.090 align:middle line:84%
They started
befriending each other,

00:03:57.090 --> 00:03:59.970 align:middle line:84%
and they started
forgiving each other.

00:03:59.970 --> 00:04:02.940 align:middle line:10%
>> Her most recent intention
experiment was done around

00:04:02.940 --> 00:04:06.690 align:middle line:10%
