00:04:59.220 --> 00:05:02.760 align:middle line:84%
Everyone involved expressed
feeling less divided.

00:05:02.760 --> 00:05:05.100 align:middle line:84%
The effects of all
these peace experiments

00:05:05.100 --> 00:05:10.170 align:middle line:84%
have been significant, both on
a mass and individual scale.

00:05:10.170 --> 00:05:14.470 align:middle line:84%
>> From 2008, I started
surveying the audience to say,

00:05:14.470 --> 00:05:16.140 align:middle line:90%
well, how was that for you?

00:05:16.140 --> 00:05:20.310 align:middle line:84%
And I was astounded
to see that people

00:05:20.310 --> 00:05:24.660 align:middle line:84%
were having extraordinary
changes in their lives.

00:05:24.660 --> 00:05:27.660 align:middle line:84%
They made up with
estranged partners.

00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:32.260 align:middle line:84%
They were more connected
to their not-so-nice boss.

00:05:32.260 --> 00:05:34.900 align:middle line:84%
