loving with everyone

00:05:39.250 --> 00:05:41.360 align:middle line:90%
they come into contact with.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:46.510 align:middle line:84%
So that involvement
in a peace experiment

00:05:46.510 --> 00:05:49.630 align:middle line:84%
reflected back on
them, and their lives

00:05:49.630 --> 00:05:52.030 align:middle line:90%
became more peaceful.

00:05:52.030 --> 00:05:57.610 align:middle line:84%
>> What is it that accounts for
these transformational effects?

00:05:57.610 --> 00:06:00.130 align:middle line:84%
>> I think that there's
several pieces here.

00:06:00.130 --> 00:06:04.820 align:middle line:84%
I think a giant piece
is intention, of course,

00:06:04.820 --> 00:06:06.520 align:middle line:90%
our ability to be creators.

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:10.000 align:middle line:84%
A second big piece
here is altruism.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:12.550 align:middle line:84%
You know, we are so
involved in self-help

00:06:12.550 --> 00:06:14.500 align:middle line:84%
in the personal
development world,

00:06:14.500 --> 00:06:17.800 align:middle line:84%
and we don't think
much about other help.

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:21.250 align:middle line:84%
But other help isn't
just a nice thing to do.

00:06:21.250 --> 00:06:25.060 align:middle line:84%
All the studies show that when
you do things for other people,

00:06:25.060 --> 00:06:28.130 align:middle line:84%
no matter how small, you
live a longer, healthier,

00:06:28.130 --> 00:06:29.170 align:middle line:90%
happier life.

00:06:29.170 --> 00:06:32.290 align:middle line:84%
Group effect-- I mean,
I've been fascinated

00:06:32.290 --> 00:06:37.600 align:middle line:84%
to see groups create
remarkable change.

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:41.020 align:middle line:84%
>> Can these effects be seen
when done in smaller groups?

00:06:41.020 --> 00:06:44.140 align:middle line:84%
Lynne first tested
this idea in 2008,

00:06:44.140 --> 00:06:46.930 align:middle line:84%
when she first began her
Power of Eight groups,

00:06:46.930 --> 00:06:49.960 align:middle line:84%
