groups send and receive

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:51.400 align:middle line:90%
healing intentions.

00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:57.340 align:middle line:84%
Since then, she has seen some
truly astounding results.

00:06:57.340 --> 00:07:00.430 align:middle line:84%
>> We experimented, and I've
experimented and now put

00:07:00.430 --> 00:07:01.990 align:middle line:90%
